{"word":"διαμνημονεύω","slug":"διαμνημονεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαμνημονεύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to call to mind, remember</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to record, mention</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>διαμνημονεύεται ἔχειν</el> <i>he is mentioned</i> as having, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}